data.description: Welcome to Mill Run and Townhouse 3906 S. Richfield Way! This fantastic home features options galore from a great SE Aurora location with choices from rent to retirement! Yes, you will not be disappointed with 3906! Reasonably priced, 3906 boasts a fantastic community with mature trees and sculpted greenbelts using Aurora's allocated water management program. The community pool is clear and cool for summer floating and the grounds are HOA maintained featuring winter snow removal. Townhome 3906 is cute as a button and ready to go! This long term owner townhome is ready for its next chapter and just right as a rental, first time home or downsizer from a larger residence. New windows frame the interior and plenty of light floods the spacious rooms. New paint throughout and just cleaned carpets leave 3906 move in ready with all the appliances included. Three bathrooms are a featured amenity in this wonderful abode. The basement is unfinished and a great palate for your favorite activities or a blank slate for your creative side! Contact the listing broker for incentives with our preferred lender featuring rate buy down, down payment assistance or ARM mortgages. Come see 3906 today and make it your next home!You won't be disappointed!
